text: aur usake saath qaid mein do yuvakon ne pravesh kiya. unamen se ek ne kahaah mainne svapn dekha hai ki sharaab nichod raha hoon aur doosare ne kahaah mainne svapn dekha hai ki apane sir ke oopar rotee uthaaye hue hoon, jisamen se pakshee kha rahe hain. hamen isaka arth (svapnaphal) bata do. ham dekh rahe hain ki tum sadaachaariyon mein se ho
